00:39:10.220 --> 00:39:12.530
I had an amazing mom.

00:39:12.530 --> 00:39:14.370
She grew up in a farm
in Denmark.

00:39:14.370 --> 00:39:17.460
World War II, the Nazis occupied
the farm, and kind of

00:39:17.460 --> 00:39:18.610
a very interesting beginning.

00:39:18.610 --> 00:39:21.610
And she just decided to leave
the farm, go travel the world,

00:39:21.610 --> 00:39:22.200
never went back.

00:39:22.200 --> 00:39:23.780
She was the only one of
her family not to.

00:39:23.780 --> 00:39:26.770
She had this attitude of--

00:39:26.770 --> 00:39:33.330
she was so positive and very
realistic about life, but also

00:39:33.330 --> 00:39:39.610
that perspective of never
give up-- persistence.

00:39:39.610 --> 00:39:40.480
Keep at it.

00:39:40.480 --> 00:39:44.690
And she did against various
obstacles along the way, and

00:39:44.690 --> 00:39:47.360
she never lost her positive
attitude.

00:39:47.360 --> 00:39:50.630
And she was also incredibly
social person, very generous.

